1. First install 'ksquirrel-libs' package:

   a) from sources
   # tar zxfv ksquirrel-libs-0.6.0.tar.gz
   # cd ksquirrel-libs-0.6.0/
   # ./configure.gnu
   # make
   # su -c 'make install'
   
   b) from binary packages
RPM  # rpm -ihv ksquirrel-libs-0.6.0.rpm
TGZ  # installpkg ksquirrel-libs-0.6.0.tgz

2. Now install Ksquirrel:

   a) from sources
   # tar zxfv ksquirrel-0.6.0.tar.gz
   # cd ksquirrel-0.6.0/
   # ./configure.gnu
   # make
   # su -c 'make install'
   
   b) from binary packages
RPM  # rpm -ihv ksquirrel-0.6.0.rpm
TGZ  # installpkg ksquirrel-0.6.0.tgz
